# DHIS2 Docker image pins per minor.
#
# Single source of truth for which exact patch we run + capture codegen against.
# The default `dhis2/core:43` tag floats — DHIS2 retags it on every patch
# release — which means committed manifests + dumps drift across time even
# without our intent. Pinning to specific tags here makes every codegen run
# reproducible: identical Docker bytes today, tomorrow, and in CI.
#
# Bumping any value here is an explicit action: re-run codegen
# (`infra/scripts/codegen_all_versions.sh N`) and commit the regen in the
# same PR. The snapshot test in packages/dhis2w-codegen/tests/ then locks
# the new tree byte-for-byte.
#
# Image tag list: https://hub.docker.com/r/dhis2/core/tags

DHIS2_V41=2.41.8.1
DHIS2_V42=2.42.4.1
DHIS2_V43=2.43.0.0
